---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contacto" description="Ponte en contacto con el Centro Sociocultural Zaidín en Granada. Dirección, teléfono, email y mapa de situación.">
  <section class="page-hero contact-hero">
    <div class="hero-pattern" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <h1>Contacto</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Estamos aquí para escucharte y atenderte</p>
  </section>

  <div class="page-content">
    <!-- Info + Map side by side on desktop -->
    <div class="contact-layout">
      <!-- Left: info cards -->
      <div class="contact-info">

        <div class="c-card c-card-accent" style="--card-accent:#059669">
          <div class="c-card-row">
            <span class="c-icon">📍</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Dirección</h3>
              <p>Calle Zurbarán nº 8</p>
              <p>18007, Granada · Barrio del Zaidín</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/K6dNXKctRxh8a5SF8" target="_blank" class="c-btn">Abrir en Google Maps →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="c-card" style="--card-accent:#2563eb">
          <div class="c-card-row">
            <span class="c-icon">📞</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Teléfono</h3>
              <p><strong>Fijo:</strong> <a href="tel:958136876">958 136 876</a></p>
              <p><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> <a href="https://wa.me/34655120590">655 12 05 90</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="c-card" style="--card-accent:#d97706">
          <div class="c-card-row">
            <span class="c-icon">✉️</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Email</h3>
              <p><a href="mailto:csazaidin@yahoo.es">csazaidin@yahoo.es</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="mailto:csazaidin@yahoo.es" class="c-btn">Enviar correo →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="c-card" style="--card-accent:#7c3aed">
          <div class="c-card-row">
            <span class="c-icon">🌐</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Redes sociales</h3>
              <p>Síguenos para estar al día de todas nuestras actividades</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="c-social">
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/csc_zaidin/" target="_blank" class="c-social-btn insta">📸 Instagram</a>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/csczaidin" target="_blank" class="c-social-btn fb">👍 Facebook</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Right: map -->
      <div class="contact-map-wrap">
        <div class="c-map-container">
          <div class="c-map-header">
            <span style="font-size:1.1rem">🏠</span> Cómo llegar
          </div>
          <div class="c-map-frame">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3178.793965223222!2d-3.603996284608774!3d37.15330497970922!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xd71fb5e20dc9381%3A0x7ca58a15c2928e57!2sC.%20Zurbar%C3%A1n%2C%208%2C%20Zaid%C3%ADn%2C%2018007%20Granada!5e0!3m2!1ses!2ses!4v1"
              width="100%" height="100%"
              style="border:0"
              allowfullscreen=""
              loading="lazy"
              referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
              title="Mapa de situación del Centro Sociocultural Zaidín"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Quick info -->
        <div class="c-hours">
          <div class="c-hours-row">
            <span>📅</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Horario de atención</strong>
              <p>Lunes a jueves de 10:00 a 14:00 y de 17:00 a 20:00</p>
              <p>Viernes de 10:00 a 14:00</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <div class="c-cta">
      <p>¿Tienes alguna pregunta o quieres colaborar con nosotros?</p>
      <p class="c-cta-small">No dudes en contactarnos. Estaremos encantados de atenderte.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/34655120590" class="c-cta-btn">💬 Escríbenos por WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .contact-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d9488 0%, #065f46 100%) !important;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .contact-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
  .contact-hero .subtitle { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); }
  .hero-pattern {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: 0.08;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 25% 25%, #fff 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 30px 30px;
  }

  .contact-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Cards */
  .contact-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .c-card {
    background: var(--w);
    border: 1px solid var(--g200);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--card-accent, var(--green));
    border-radius: var(--r);
    padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .c-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }
  .c-card-accent { border-left-width: 4px; }
  .c-card-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }
  .c-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .c-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
    color: var(--g700);
  }
  .c-card p {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--g500);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .c-card a { color: var(--green); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
  .c-card a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .c-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.65rem;
    padding: 0.45rem 1rem;
    background: var(--g50);
    color: var(--g600) !important;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .c-btn:hover { background: var(--green); color: #fff !important; text-decoration: none !important; }

  .c-social { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 0.65rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .c-social-btn {
    padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none !important;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .c-social-btn.insta {
    background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e !important;
  }
  .c-social-btn.insta:hover {
    background: #f59e0b; color: #fff !important;
  }
  .c-social-btn.fb {
    background: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af !important;
  }
  .c-social-btn.fb:hover {
    background: #2563eb; color: #fff !important;
  }

  /* Map */
  .contact-map-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .c-map-container {
    background: var(--w);
    border: 1px solid var(--g200);
    border-radius: var(--r);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .c-map-header {
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--g700);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--g100);
  }
  .c-map-frame {
    width: 100%;
    height: 320px;
  }
  .c-map-frame iframe {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  /* Hours */
  .c-hours {
    background: var(--green);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: var(--r);
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .c-hours-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .c-hours-row span { font-size: 1.3rem; line-height: 1.3; }
  .c-hours-row strong { display: block; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .c-hours-row p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
  }

  /* Bottom CTA */
  .c-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding: 2rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--g200);
  }
  .c-cta p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--g500); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .c-cta-small { font-size: 0.9rem !important; color: var(--g400) !important; margin-bottom: 1rem !important; }
  .c-cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    background: var(--green);
    color: #fff !important;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none !important;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .c-cta-btn:hover { background: #047857; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .contact-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .contact-hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
    .c-map-frame { height: 380px; }
  }
</style>
